        </div>
        <div class="stat-item">
          <h4 class="stat-number">10</h4>
          <p class="stat-label">Countries Reached</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="testimonials-carousel">
        <div class="testimonial-item">
          <p>
            "API's training has transformed our community." - Community Leader,
            South Sudan
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
</section>

  <section id="get-involved" class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Join the Movement!</h2>
      <p>Be a part of building a peaceful and prosperous Africa.</p>
      <div class="cta-buttons">
        <a href="#" class="cta-button primary-button">Donate Today</a>
        <a href="#" class="cta-button secondary-button">Volunteer Now</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="blog" class="blog-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Latest Updates</h2>
      <div class="blog-grid">
        <div class="blog-post">
          <div class="post-thumbnail">
            <img
              src="https://via.placeholder.com/600x400"
              alt="Blog Post 1"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="post-content">
            <h3 class="post-title">Empowering Women in Peacebuilding</h3>
            <p class="post-excerpt">Learn about API's recent initiative...</p>
            <a href="#" class="read-more-link">Read More</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="blog-post">
          <div class="post-thumbnail">
            <img
              src="https://via.placeholder.com/600x400"
              alt="Blog Post 2"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="post-content">
            <h3 class="post-title">Youth Leading Sustainable Development</h3>
            <p class="post-excerpt">Discover how young people are driving...</p>
            <a href="#" class="read-more-link">Read More</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer id="contact">
    <div class="container footer-content">
      <div class="footer-col">
        <h3>Contact Us</h3>
        <ul class="contact-info">
          <li>
            <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> Email: info@africapeaceinitiative.org
          </li>
          <li><i class="fas fa-phone"></i> Phone: +254 705 329 860</li>
          <li>
            <i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i> Address: 12 Peace Street, Nairobi,
